@denise123_cohen @UKCoachleader @AimeeRobson4 @amy_makler @kennygibsonnhs I understood that and I don‚Äôt disagree that compassion is important and helps to an extent.

@denise123_cohen @UKCoachleader @AimeeRobson4 @amy_makler @kennygibsonnhs But i think the essence of that phrase is that we are not all in it together, because of inequality.
